

    Tools Used:

        Replaced Azure AI Search with Azure Java SDK

        Used Apache Lucene for indexing instead of Python solutions

    Design Patterns:

        Applied Factory pattern for processor creation

        Utilized Stream API for data manipulation

    Strong Typing:

        Benefited from Java's static typing for data validation

        Created well-defined model classes

